### Music Library API Test File
### Use with VS Code REST Client Extension or IntelliJ HTTP Client

### ====================== ADMIN SERVICE ======================

### Add Song
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/songs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "songName": "Shape of You",
  "musicDirector": "Ed Sheeran",
  "singer": "Ed Sheeran",
  "releaseDate": "2017-01-06",
  "albumName": "Divide",
  "songType": "FREE",
  "songStatus": "AVAILABLE"
}

### Get All Songs
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/songs

### Get Song by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/songs/1

### Update Song Status
PUT http://localhost:8080/admin/songs/1/status?status=NOTAVAILABLE

### Delete Song
DELETE http://localhost:8080/admin/songs/1


### ====================== USER SERVICE ======================

### Register User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "username": "johndoe",
  "password": "password123",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "mobile": "1234567890",
  "address1": "123 Main St",
  "city": "New York"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "johndoe",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Available Songs (requires token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/songs
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Search Songs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/songs/search?query=Ed
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Create Playlist
POST http://localhost:8080/api/playlists
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "playlistName": "My Favorites"
}

### Get User Playlists
GET http://localhost:8080/api/playlists
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Add Song to Playlist
POST http://localhost:8080/api/playlists/1/songs?songId=1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Playlist Songs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/playlists/1/songs
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Play Song
POST http://localhost:8080/api/player/play/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Stop Playback
POST http://localhost:8080/api/player/stop
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Shuffle Playlist
POST http://localhost:8080/api/player/shuffle/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE


### ====================== NOTIFICATION SERVICE ======================

### Get All Notifications
GET http://localhost:8080/notify/all
